{"word":"ἄρσις","slug":"ἄρσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄρσις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:αἴρω'><el>αἴρω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a raising</i> of the foot in walking, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in Prosody, <i>arsis</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <i>thesis</i>.<p/></div>"}]}